definitions.definition: A tabular schedule of events with the times at which they occur , especially times of arrivals and departures .
examples: The timetable has been changed several times since it was first announced.

definitions.definition: A schedule of arrivals and departures published in book or booklet form, or as a pamphlet , and available to travellers , either free or for a charge.
